column16: Justin Bour grounds out to first baseman Chris Carter.
Martin Prado lines out sharply to center fielder Kirk Nieuwenhuis.
Derek Dietrich triples (3) on a sharp line drive to right fielder Alex Presley.   Derek Dietrich scores.  Throwing error by second baseman Yadiel Rivera.
Jeff Samardzija lines out to second baseman Jemile Weeks.
Trevor Brown singles on a ground ball to center fielder Jon Jay.   Hunter Pence scores.
Angel Pagan grounds out softly, third baseman Brett Wallace to first baseman Wil Myers.   Hunter Pence to 2nd.
Hunter Pence singles on a line drive to center fielder Jon Jay.   Brandon Belt scores.
Brandon Crawford grounds out to first baseman Wil Myers.
Brandon Belt triples (1) on a ground ball to right fielder Matt Kemp.   Joe Panik scores.    Matt Duffy scores.
Matt Duffy singles on a ground ball to left fielder Melvin Upton.   Joe Panik to 3rd.
Joe Panik singles on a line drive to left fielder Melvin Upton.
Denard Span grounds into a force out, shortstop Alexei Ramirez to second baseman Jemile Weeks.   Jeff Samardzija out at 2nd.
Jeff Samardzija singles on a fly ball to right fielder Matt Kemp.   Brandon Belt scores.    Angel Pagan scores.    Trevor Brown to 3rd.
